{"id":"AJIAKESI2","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["私の素晴らしい記憶\n\n<size=45>その二 栄光の意味<\/size>",1]]},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"エイジャックス、お前というやつは…！ ","nameColor":"#a9f548","bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":203080,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"私は正論を言っただけですよ。真正面から戦うより夜戦で挑んだ方が勝率が高いですもの。","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":202030,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"そもそも助けを求める味方の拠点を無視するのは、ロイヤルネイビーの栄光に泥を塗る行為ではないか！","actor":203080,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"エクセター先輩こそ、栄光に拘りすぎなのではなくて？あの場面で味方の戦力を分割するなんて、先輩は一人で敵の主力と戦いたいのですか？そうしたければ止めはしませんけど♪","actor":202030,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"say":"エクセターとエイジャックスは相変わらず言い争っている。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"say":"エイジャックスの作戦案は驚くほど合理的かつ正確である。とはいえ、合理的すぎるがゆえに一部の名誉や格式を重んじる子とはどうも反りが合わないらしい。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"くっ…！これ以上言い争っても無駄だ。あとは指揮官の判断を仰ぐ！","actor":203080,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"逃げるんですか？むしろ栄光なる転進というべきかしら？","actor":202030,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"say":"なにより相手が反論すればするほど本人がついつい煽るため、結果的にややこしくなることも多い…","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"say":"エクセター先輩にはちゃんと謝りましたわよ。いつものことですので。","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":202030,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"エクセター先輩は説得しても聞かないタイプですから、延々と説明するより一度怒らせてから折れてもらったほうが早いのではなくて？","actor":202030,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"まあ、それも指揮官がそこで止めに入ってくれることを織り込んだ作戦ですけど♪","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"options":[{"content":"だからといって、そこまで先輩をいじらなくても……","flag":1}],"actor":202030,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"あら、秘書艦の私に肩入れしないのですね。評価してあげます。","actor":202030,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"普段は優しいのに、こういう時はちゃんと指揮官として振る舞うのですね。","actor":202030,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"……だから好きですわ。うふふ♪","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"actor":202030,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}}],"fadeOut":1.5,"fadeType":2,"fadein":1.5,"mode":2,"once":true}